{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 HOW TO USE: Select items and then select an envelope lane. Run this script to create pooled automation items for all of your selected media items. The duplicated automation items are scaled in length to conform to the first item. In this way both fade-ins and fade-out will align with item starts and ends. To disable this stretching/squashing behaviour, delete lines 74 and 75\par}
}

